
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
BATCH RESIZE FILES:
-------------------
* Set bash input/output file locations
* Run bash script


-------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Images must have height/width both devisible by 2
* -i = input files path
* -y = output file path
* framerate = defaults to 25
* -r = set frame rate
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

ffmpeg -framerate 10 -i /home/antz/Pictures/sec_vid/security/%d.jpg -r 15 -y security.mp4
